le will call your people.  We'll do lunch.<br><br>/ramble off <p><BR>Brampton Macdougal:<BR> Enchanter, and Master of the Area Mezz!<BR>  -- You begin casting mesmerization...<BR>  -- YOU are stunned!<BR>  ....aw, crap.</p><span class=m><i></i></span><hr size=1><span class=m> Posts: <b>12</b>  </span></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td colspan=2><table cellpadding=8 cellspacing=0 width=100%><tr><td nowrap width=20% valign=top><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub95.ezboard.com/uraidal.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Raidal</A> </span><br> <span class=usertitle>A Shadow at Heart</span><br> </td><td valign=top width=80% class=m><span class=title>   Re: Different Aid Station Revisited</span><br><span class=m><font color=#778899>Posted: 3/19/02 1:30:39 am</font>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>   &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=http://pub95.ezboard.com/febonmoonfrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=15.topic&index=1><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/reply.gif border=0 width=20 height=20 alt="reply to this message" align=absmiddle></a>   <hr size=1> I am up for it. I could camp gator scale leggings and sleeves to give away. <br><br>Raidal Deepwounder <br>Beastlord of the 31st hunt(woot made it out of hell) <p></p><span class=m><i></i></span><hr size=1><span class=m> Posts: <b>76</b>  </span></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td colspan=2><table cellpadding=8 cellspacing=0 width=100%><tr><td nowrap width=20% valign=top><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub95.ezboard.com/udadalanlyfrender.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Dadalan Lyfrender</A> </span><br> <span class=usertitle>Raid Lieutenant</span><br> <BR><img src=http://www.bestbuypcs.com/topimages/Dad_headshot.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top width=80% class=m><span class=title>   Re: Different Aid Station Revisited</span><br><span class=m><font color=#778899>Posted: 3/19/02 11:03:30 am</font>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;